/* --------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * Instructions
 *
 * Notes:
 * o CASEFAIL is generated by the compiler whenever it tests an "irrefutable"
 *   pattern which fails.  If we don't see too many of these, we could
 *   optimise out the redundant test.
 * ------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

